Naomi Brockwell - What is Zencash_.mp4.description: What is Zencash? This privacy-oriented blockchain platform that incorporates possibly the most secure messaging system in existence will be celebrating its 1-year anniversary soon, so I chatted to co-founder Rob Viglione about the future of Zencash and why privacy is important now more
